OL,3,CAlmost all county councils in England
OL,4,Cto raise council tax by maximum amount
OL,6,FIn her first Budget last Autumn,
OL,7,FChancellor Rachel Reeves announced a
OL,8,Flarger than expected pot of money for
OL,9,Fcouncils, with an increase of #1.3bn
OL,10,Fin 2025/26, including #600m for adult
OL,11,Fand children's social care.
OL,13,FBut at the same time, Reeves also put
OL,14,Fup National Insurance contributions
OL,15,Ffor employers by 1.2 percentage
OL,16,Fpoints, and raised the minimum wage -
OL,17,Fwhich has further stretched already
OL,18,Fstruggling social care providers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
