OL,6,FReeves insists she recognises "the
OL,7,Fhuge pressure local authorities are
OL,8,Funder after a decade of cuts and
OL,9,Fausterity."
OL,11,F"We can't turn everything around
OL,12,Fovernight, but we did make more money
OL,13,Favailable for local authorities in the
OL,14,FBudget last year", she said.
OL,16,FITV News spent time with Kent County
OL,17,FCouncil, visiting one care home where
OL,18,Fstaffing costs have gone up by 11%,
OL,19,Fbut the council is only able to help
OL,20,Fcover 4% of that increase.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
