OL,3,CAlmost all county councils in England
OL,4,Cto raise council tax by maximum amount
OL,6,FPeter Oakford, the Conservative Deputy
OL,7,FLeader of Kent County Council, said it
OL,8,Fwas "horrible" to have to keep putting
OL,9,Fcouncil tax up.
OL,11,F"I'm a resident of Kent... it impacts
OL,12,Feverybody, we've done it year on year,
OL,13,Fcouncil tax has gone through the
OL,14,Froof", he said.
OL,16,FIn the Budget the government announced
OL,17,F#600m would be targeted at councils
OL,18,Fwith the largest populations and the
OL,19,Fhighest levels of deprivation - which
OL,20,Fmeans the funding is mainly going to
OL,21,Furban areas.
