OL,3,CAlmost all county councils in England
OL,4,Cto raise council tax by maximum amount
OL,6,FThey said that the total funding for
OL,7,FEnglish councils worth #69bn
OL,8,Frepresented a 6% cash terms increase
OL,9,Fin Core Spending Power on 2024-25. "No
OL,10,Fcouncil will see a decrease in their
OL,11,FCore Spending Power, with the majority
OL,12,Fseeing a marked real terms increase
OL,13,Fcompared to 2024-25 when we confirm
OL,14,Fthe exact numbers for each council
OL,15,Fnext week.
OL,17,F"This is all part of an uplift of more
OL,18,Fthan #5 billion in guaranteed funding
OL,19,Ffor local government this year for
OL,20,Flocal services."
