OL,6,FThey added that families relied on
OL,7,Fservices such as social care and so
OL,8,Fthere was additional funding for that
OL,9,Fand to help councils cover the
OL,10,Fnational insurance increase.
OL,12,FHowever, in Kent - they said that only
OL,13,Fcovered direct council staff, but they
OL,14,Fcommissioned external providers for
OL,15,Fcare who did not get the same
OL,16,Fcompensation.
